 Kenya, the Kanu government does. <#/>The Opposition does not have the power to carry out those actions the bishops requested, the Government does. <#/>When the Government is asked to ensure a toning down of inflammatory statements or dissociation from th
e most outrageous of Ministers' remarks, Kenyans have the right to expect the Government to heed this request. <X_>}{\v\f0\fs24\lang2057 What they get instead is a diatribe against the Opposition.
