\par This newspaper has no particular brief for the Opposition though we grow weary of saying it, we say it again: If the Opposition has been responsible for the clashes, bring them to court.
\par Meanwhile, Kenyans would be more interested in hearing of concrete action to stem rising violence in the new areas of conflagration. }{\f0\fs24\lang2057 </X>
